{"tid":1534621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生可否搞個朝早版 十點鐘對街大嗌?","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:05:29.000Z","uid":64757,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b60abcafe1bc537bc70ef0f4dad3348d0f0156","tid":1534621,"uid":64757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"還掂都罷緊課   釋放下情緒  百利而無一害"},{"pid":"4e805e2da2e8c9a52a188cc38270f04d824ccc8e","tid":1534621,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b3fd801af780a2bad110db7b0cf0a1412f5edd","tid":1534621,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"81d67e7bfaf3ef163b3353a99f839a7d8daf2654","tid":1534621,"uid":13514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"每逢小息全校一齊嗌"},{"pid":"c6e7045714e77a68c3ac3ca55040208eefe72da8","tid":1534621,"uid":260744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"幾點都好， 想叫就叫， 無需約定"},{"pid":"4792cf787529436a4ae4cce9adafa75d29ad6b1e","tid":1534621,"uid":64757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"學校區既地方  如果一齊嗌  效果會否更突出?"},{"pid":"4a010220c47ed9be15d2e0ae1e9e9c8027d7b982","tid":1534621,"uid":67332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:39:28.000Z","msg":"小息：操場，午息：校門"},{"pid":"407234f363281db212e3644ff7259c6c938006cb","tid":1534621,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img